With the TOPGREENER skill for Alexa, you can now control a wide range of home automation devices such as switches, dimmers, and outlets with your voice.

Setup: 
(1) Download our "TOPGREENER" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2) Launch the app and register a new account;
(3) Turn on TOPGREENER devices and connect them with “TOPGREENER” application;
(4) Note: You can rename the devices within TOPGREENER application. Renaming an ON/OFF switch to “Livingroom Light”, then Echo will get that same name after discovering the device;
(5) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(6) Search the Alexa Skills directory for "TOPGREENER";
(7) Click Enable skill (TOPGREENER), follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(8) Talk to Echo "“Alexa, discover devices”. Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed";
(9) Now you are ready for device voice control.
Voice Control Methods:
(1) Device Name
(2) Scene
(3) Group

